{"word":"διαμπάξ","slug":"διαμπάξ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διαμπάξ</b></el>  (diampa/c) adverb<p/><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:strengthened'>strengthd.</a> for <a href='S:διά'><el>διά</el></a>\n<p/><i>right through, through and through</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; also <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/>"}]}